ng>save multiple shipping and billing addresses</strong> on their account and choose which ones to use at checkout and cart pages.' => 'Mijozlarga o&#39;z hisoblarida <strong>bir nechta yuk va to&#39;lov manzillarini saqlashga</strong> va to&#39;lov va savat sahifalarida qaysilaridan foydalanishni tanlashiga ruxsat bering.','Get this add-on &mdash; 59 EUR' => 'Ushbu qo&#39;shimchani oling - 59 EUR','Simplified EU-VAT validation for your store.' => 'Do&#39;koningiz uchun soddalashtirilgan EI-QQS tekshiruvi.','Collect and <strong>validate EU VAT numbers at the checkout page</strong>, removes tax charges on reverse charge basis and confirms customer location when needed.' => '<strong>Hisob-kitob sahifasida YI QQS raqamlarini to&#39;plang va tasdiqlang</strong> , teskari to&#39;lov asosida soliq to&#39;lovlarini olib tashlaydi va kerak bo&#39;lganda mijozning joylashgan joyini tasdiqlaydi.','Get this add-on &mdash; 39 EUR' => 'Ushbu qo&#39;shimchani oling - 39 EUR','All add-ons are sold separately and require the <strong>Fluid Checkout Lite</strong> plugin to be installed and activated, except when noted.' => 'Barcha qo&#39;shimchalar alohida sotiladi va <strong>Fluid Checkout Lite</strong> plaginini o&#39;rnatish va faollashtirishni talab qiladi, qayd qilingan hollar bundan mustasno.','Select an image' => 'Rasm tanlang','<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Log in to your account</a> to get your license key, or <a href="%s" target="_blank">purchase a new license key</a>.' => 'Litsenziya kalitini olish uchun <a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">hisobingizga kiring</a> yoki <a href="%s" target="_blank">yangi litsenziya kalitini sotib oling</a> .','Valid until %s.' => '%s gacha amal qiladi.','Expired on %s.' => 'Muddati %s da tugagan.','<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Log in to your account</a> to renew your license key and continue to receive updates and support.' => 'Litsenziya kalitingizni yan