yuk tashish; yetkazib berish','Select position where to display the shipping costs and calculator on the cart page.' => 'Savat sahifasida yuk narxi va kalkulyator ko&#39;rsatiladigan joyni tanlang.','Display as a cart section' => 'Savat qismi sifatida ko&#39;rsatish','Cross-sells' => 'O&#39;zaro sotuvlar','Select position where to display the cross-sells section on the cart page.' => 'Savat sahifasida o&#39;zaro sotuvlar bo&#39;limi ko&#39;rsatiladigan joyni tanlang.','Before the cart actions' => 'Arava harakatlaridan oldin','After the cart actions' => 'Arava harakatlaridan keyin','Layout of cross-sell items on the cart page.' => 'Savat sahifasida o&#39;zaro sotiladigan mahsulotlarning joylashuvi.','Optimized horizontal cross-sells layout' => 'Optimallashtirilgan gorizontal o&#39;zaro savdo tartibi','Theme\'s cross-sells layout' => 'Mavzuning o&#39;zaro savdo tartibi','Number of cross-sell items to display on the cart page' => 'Savat sahifasida ko&#39;rsatiladigan o&#39;zaro sotiladigan narsalar soni','Trust symbols &amp; badges' => 'Ishonch belgilari va nishonlar','Add widget areas to the cart page' => 'Savat sahifasiga vidjet maydonlarini qo&#39;shing','These widget areas are used to add trust symbols and trust badges on the cart page.' => 'Ushbu vidjet maydonlari arava sahifasiga ishonch belgilari va ishonch nishonlarini qo&#39;shish uchun ishlatiladi.','Checkout' => 'Ro&#39;yxatdan o&#39;chirilish','Layout &amp; design' => 'Joylashtirish va dizayn','Checkout layout' => 'Chiqish tartibi','Design template' => 'Dizayn shablon','General styles for the checkout steps, order summary and other sections. Might also apply to other pages such as the Cart, Order Received and View Order pages.' => 'To&#39;lov bosqichlari, buyurtma xulosasi va boshqa bo&#39;limlar uchun umumiy uslublar. Savat, Qabul qilingan buyurtma va Buyurtmani ko&#39;rish sahifalari kabi boshqa sahifalarga ham tegishli bo&#39;lishi mumkin.','Dark mode' => 'Qorong&#39;i rejim','Enable dark mode' => 'Qorong&#39;i rejimni yoqing','Header and footer templates' => 'Sarlavha va altbilgi shablonlari','We recommend using the distraction free header and footer to avoid distractions at the checkout page. <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/cart-abandonment" target="_blank">Read the research about cart abandonment</a>.' => 'Hisob-kitob sahifasida chalg&#39;itmaslik uchun biz chalg&#39;itmaydigan sarlavha va altbilgidan foydalanishni tavsiya qilamiz. <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/cart-abandonment" target="_blank">Aravadan voz kechish haqidagi tadqiqotni o&#39;qing</a> .','Logo image' => 'Logotip tasviri','Choose an image to be displayed on the checkout page header. Only applies when using the distraction free header and footer.' => 'To&#39;lov sahifasi sarlavhasida ko&#39;rsatiladigan rasmni tanlang. Faqat chalg&#39;itmaydigan sarlavha va altbilgidan foydalanganda amal qiladi.','Header background color' => 'Sarlavha fon rangi','Choose a background color for the checkout page header. Only applies when using the distraction free header and footer.' => 'Hisob-kitob sahifasi sarlavhasi uchun fon rangini tanlang. Faqat chalg&#39;itmaydigan sarlavha va altbilgidan foydalanganda amal qiladi.','HTML color value. ie: #f3f3f3' => 'HTML rang qiymati. ya&#39;ni: #f3f3f3','Page background color' => 'Sahifa fon rangi','Choose a background color for the checkout page. Color is applied to the <em>body</em> element.' => 'Hisob-kitob sahifasi uchun fon rangini tanlang. Rang <em>tananing</em> elementiga qo&#39;llaniladi.','Footer background color' => 'Altbilgi fon rangi','Choose a background color for the checkout page footer. Only applies when using the distraction free header and footer.' => 'Hisob-kitob sahifasi altbilgisi uchun fon rangini tanlang. Faqat chalg&#39;itmaydigan sarlavha va altbilgidan foydalanganda amal qiladi.','Checkout elements' => 'Hisoblash elementlari','Progress bar' => 'Rivojlanish paneli','Display the checkout progress bar when using multi-step checkout layout' => 'Ko&#39;p bosqichli to&#39;lov tartibidan foydalanganda to&#39;lov jarayoni satrini ko&#39;rsating','Make the checkout progress bar stay visible while scrolling' => 'Oʻtkazish paytida toʻlov jarayoni satri koʻrinadigan boʻlsin','Express checkout' => 'Ekspress to&#39;lov','Enable the express checkout section' => 'Ekspress to&#39;lov bo&#39;limini yoqing','Displays the express checkout section at checkout when supported payment gateways have this feature enabled.' => 'Qo&#39;llab-quvvatlanadigan to&#39;lov shlyuzlarida bu xususiyat yoqilgan bo&#39;lsa, to&#39;lov vaqtida tezkor to&#39;lov bo&#39;limini ko&#39;rsatadi.','Display express checkout buttons in one line for larger screens' => 'Kattaroq ekranlar uchun tezkor to&#39;lov tugmalarini bir qatorda ko&#39;rsating','Ignore additional checkout required fields when paying with a compatible express checkout payment gateway' => 'Mos keladigan tezkor to&#39;lov shlyuzi bilan to&#39;lashda qo&#39;shimcha to&#39;lov talab qilinadigan maydonlarga e&#39;tibor bermang','Make the order summary stay visible while scrolling' => 'O&#39;tkazish paytida buyurtma xulosasini ko&#39;rinadigan qilib qo&#39;ying','Choose a background color for the order summary section.' => 'Buyurtma xulosasi bo&#39;limi uchun fon rangini tanlang.','Highlight the order totals row in the order summary table' => 'Buyurtmalar sarhisobi jadvalidagi buyurtma jami qatorini ajratib ko&#39;rsating','Most useful when the order summary section does not have a highlighted background color. Might also apply to the Cart, Order Received and View Order pages when using Fluid Checkout PRO.' => 'Buyurtma xulosasi bo&#39;limida ta&#39;kidlangan fon rangi bo&#39;lmasa, eng foydali bo&#39;ladi. Fluid Checkout PRO-dan foydalanganda Savat, Qabul qilingan buyurtma va Buyurtmani ko&#39;rish sahifalariga ham tegishli bo&#39;lishi mumkin.','Action link on the order summary at checkout.' => 'To‘lov vaqtida buyurtma xulosasidagi amallar havolasi.','Edit cart link' => 'Savatga havolani tahrirlash','Cart items count' => 'Savatdagi buyumlar soni','Link to shop page' => 'Do&#39;kon sahifasiga havola','Cart items' => 'Savat buyumlari','Enable options to edit cart items on the checkout page' => 'Toʻlov sahifasida savat elementlarini tahrirlash parametrlarini yoqing','Allow customers to change product quantities or removing items directly at the checkout page.' => 'Mijozlarga to&#39;g&#39;ridan-to&#39;g&#39;ri to&#39;lov sahifasida mahsulot miqdorini o&#39;zgartirish yoki narsalarni olib tashlashga ruxsat bering.','Hide cart items errors at the checkout page' => 'To&#39;lov sahifasida savatdagi xatolarni yashirish','Do not display the cart items errors message at the top of the checkout page. When submitting the checkout form to complete the purchase, these error messages will always be displayed.' => 'To&#39;lov sahifasining yuqori qismida savat elementlari xato xabarini ko&#39;rsatmang. Xaridni yakunlash uchun to&#39;lov shaklini yuborayotganda, bu xato xabarlari doimo ko&#39;rsatiladi.','Place order' => 'Buyurtma berish','Define the position to display "Place order" and terms checkbox section.' => '&quot;Buyurtmani joylashtirish&quot; va shartlarni belgilash katakchasini ko&#39;rsatadigan joyni belgilang.','Some options might not be compatible with some plugins and themes.' => 'Ba&#39;zi variantlar ba&#39;zi plaginlar va mavzular bilan mos kelmasligi mumkin.','Below the payment section' => 'To&#39;lov bo&#39;limi ostida','Below the order summary' => 'Buyurtma xulosasi ostida','Both below the payment section and the order summary' => 'Toʻlov boʻlimi va buyurtma xulosasi ostida','Add widget areas to the checkout page' => 'Hisob-kitob sahifasiga vidjet maydonlarini qo&#39;shing','These widget areas are used to add trust symbols and trust badges on the checkout page.' => 'Ushbu vidjet maydonlari to&#39;lov sahifasiga ishonch belgilari va ishonch nishonlarini qo&#39;shish uchun ishlatiladi.','Display checkout sidebar widgets only when viewing the last checkout step on mobile devices when using multi-step checkout layout' => 'Ko‘p bosqichli to‘lov tartibidan foydalanilganda, mobil qurilmalarda faqat oxirgi to‘lov bosqichini ko‘rishda to‘lov yon paneli vidjetlarini ko‘rsatish','Enable integrated coupon code section' => 'Birlashtirilgan kupon kodi bo&#39;limini yoqing','Only applicable if use of coupon codes are enabled in the WooCommerce settings.' => 'WooCommerce sozlamalarida kupon kodlaridan foydalanish yoqilgan bo&#39;lsagina amal qiladi.','Display the coupon codes section title' => 'Kupon kodlari bo&#39;limi sarlavhasini ko&#39;rsating','Only applicable when coupon code is displayed as a separate section on the checkout or cart pages.' => 'Faqat kupon kodi to&#39;lov yoki savat sahifalarida alohida bo&#39;lim sifatida ko&#39;rsatilganda amal qiladi.','Select position where to display the coupon codes section on the checkout page.' => 'To&#39;lov sahifasida kupon kodlari bo&#39;limi ko&#39;rsatiladigan joyni tanlang.','Before the checkout steps' => 'To&#39;lov bosqichlaridan oldin','As a substep before payment methods' => 'To&#39;lov usullaridan oldin kichik qadam sifatida','As a substep after payment methods' => 'To&#39;lov usullaridan keyin pastki qadam sifatida','Select style of the "apply coupon" button. Only applicable when the coupon code section is displayed "Before the checkout steps" on the checkout page, or "Before the cart items section" on the cart page.' => '&quot;Kuponni qo&#39;llash&quot; tugmasi uslubini tanlang. Faqat kupon kodi boʻlimi toʻlov sahifasida “Toʻlov bosqichlaridan oldin” yoki savat sahifasida “Savatchalar boʻlimidan oldin” koʻrsatilganda amal qiladi.','Default button style' => 'Standart tugma uslubi','"Add" link button' => '&quot;Qo&#39;shish&quot; havola tugmasi','Checkout fields' => 'Hisob-kitob maydonlari','Optional fields' => 'Ixtiyoriy maydonlar','Hide optional fields behind a link button' => 'Ixtiyoriy maydonlarni havola tugmasi orqasiga yashiring','It is recommended to keep this option checked to reduce the number of open input fields, <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/checkout-flow-average-form-fields#1-address-line-2--company-name-can-safely-be-collapsed-behind-a-link" target="_blank">read the research</a>.' => 'Ochiq kirish maydonlari sonini kamaytirish uchun ushbu parametrni belgilab qo&#39;yish tavsiya etiladi, <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/checkout-flow-average-form-fields#1-address-line-2--company-name-can-safely-be-collapsed-behind-a-link" target="_blank">tadqiqotni o&#39;qing</a> .','Do not hide "Address line 2" fields behind a link button' => 'Bog&#39;lanish tugmasi orqasida &quot;Manzil qatori 2&quot; maydonlarini yashirmang','Recommended only when most customers actually need the "Address line 2" field, or when getting the right shipping address is crucial (ie. if delivering food and other perishable products).' => 'Aksariyat mijozlarga “Manzil qatori 2” maydoni kerak bo‘lganda yoki to‘g‘ri yetkazib berish manzili muhim bo‘lganda (ya’ni, oziq-ovqat va boshqa tez buziladigan mahsulotlarni yetkazib berishda) tavsiya etiladi.','Display the "Add" link buttons in lowercase' => '&quot;Qo&#39;shish&quot; havola tugmalarini kichik harflar bilan ko&#39;rsating','Make the labels of optional field "Add" link button as <code>lowercase</code> (ie. "Add phone number" instead of "Add Phone Number"). This option also affects the link buttons for coupon code fields.' => 'Ixtiyoriy maydonning yorliqlarini &quot;Qo&#39;shish&quot; havola tugmasini <code>lowercase</code> qilib qo&#39;ying (ya&#39;ni, &quot;Telefon raqamini qo&#39;shish&quot; o&#39;rniga &quot;Telefon raqamini qo&#39;shish&quot;). Ushbu parametr kupon kodi maydonlari uchun havola tugmalariga ham ta&#39;sir qiladi.','Billing address' => 'To&#39;lovchi; to&#39;lovni qabul qiladigan manzil','Select position where to display the billing address section on the checkout page.' => 'To‘lov sahifasida to‘lov manzili bo‘limi ko‘rsatiladigan joyni tanlang.','As a step before shipping' => 'Yuk tashishdan oldin qadam sifatida','As a sub-step before the shipping address section' => 'Yuk tashish manzili bo&#39;limidan oldingi kichik qadam sifatida','As a sub-step after the shipping address section' => 'Yuk tashish manzili bo&#39;limidan keyin pastki bosqich sifatida','As a step after shipping' => 'Yuk tashishdan keyingi qadam sifatida','As a sub-step before the payment section' => 'To&#39;lov bo&#39;limidan oldingi kichik qadam sifatida','Force billing and shipping addresses to the same (single section)' => 'To‘lov va yetkazib berish manzillarini bir xil (bitta bo‘lim) ga majburlash','Checkbox for "Same as shipping/billing address" checked by default' => 'Sukut bo&#39;yicha &quot;Yuk tashish/to&#39;lov manzili bilan bir xil&quot; katagiga belgi qo&#39;yilgan','The checkbox "Same as shiping address" will start as checked by default when the shipping address section is displayed first. <br>The checkbox "Same as billing address" will start as checked by default when the billing address section is displayed first. <br> It is recommended to leave this option checked as to significantly reduce the number of open input fields at checkout, <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/checkout-flow-average-form-fields#3-default-billing--shipping-and-hide-the-fields-entirely" target="_blank">read the research</a>.' => 'Yuk tashish manzili bo&#39;limi birinchi bo&#39;lib ko&#39;rsatilganda &quot;Yuk tashish manzili bilan bir xil&quot; katakchasi sukut bo&#39;yicha belgilangan tarzda boshlanadi.<br> Hisob-kitob manzili bo&#39;limi birinchi bo&#39;lib ko&#39;rsatilganda, &quot;To&#39;lov manzili bilan bir xil&quot; katakchasi sukut bo&#39;yicha belgilangan tarzda boshlanadi.<br> To&#39;lov paytida ochiq kirish maydonlari sonini sezilarli darajada kamaytirish uchun ushbu parametrni belgilab qo&#39;yish tavsiya etiladi, <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/checkout-flow-average-form-fields#3-default-billing--shipping-and-hide-the-fields-entirely" target="_blank">tadqiqotni o&#39;qing</a> .','Highlight the billing address section in the checkout form' => 'To&#39;lov shaklida to&#39;lov manzili bo&#39;limini belgilang','Shipping address' => 'Yetkazib berish manzili','Highlight the shipping address section in the checkout form' => 'To&#39;lov shaklida etkazib berish manzili bo&#39;limini belgilang','Shipping methods' => 'Yuk tashish usullari','Choose in which position to display the shipping methods section.' => 'Yuk tashish usullari bo&#39;limini qaysi holatda ko&#39;rsatishni tanlang.','Before shipping address' => 'Yuk tashish manzilidan oldin','After shipping address' => 'Yuk tashish manzilidan keyin','Prevent automatic selection of the first shipping method' => 'Birinchi yuk tashish usulini avtomatik tanlashni oldini olish','When enabled, the first shipping method available will not be automatically selected when no other shipping method was previously selected for each shipping package. <br>This option will be automatically enabled if the option for clearing the selected shipping method is enabled for the Local Pickup feature.' => 'Yoqilganda, har bir jo‘natish paketi uchun avval boshqa jo‘natish usuli tanlanmagan bo‘lsa, mavjud bo‘lgan birinchi yetkazib berish usuli avtomatik ravishda tanlanmaydi.<br> Mahalliy olib ketish funksiyasi uchun tanlangan jo‘natish usulini tozalash opsiyasi yoqilgan bo‘lsa, bu parametr avtomatik ravishda yoqiladi.','Local pickup' => 'Mahalliy olib ketish','Removes shipping address section when a local pickup shipping method is selected.' => 'Mahalliy olib ketish usuli tanlanganda yetkazib berish manzili boʻlimini olib tashlaydi.','Replaces the shipping address with the pickup point location when a local pickup shipping method is selected.' => 'Mahalliy olib ketish usuli tanlanganda jo‘natish manzilini qabul qilish punkti joyi bilan almashtiradi.','Show option to clear shipping methods in the pickup location substep' => 'Olib ketish joyi quyi bo‘limida yuk tashish usullarini tozalash variantini ko‘rsatish','Show a link button on the pickup location substep to clear the chosen shipping methods. This can be used to allow showing the shipping address section again if a local pickup method was previously selected.' => 'Tanlangan jo‘natish usullarini tozalash uchun olib ketish joyi pastki qadamida havola tugmasini ko‘rsating. Agar avval mahalliy olib ketish usuli tanlangan boʻlsa, undan yuk manzili boʻlimini yana koʻrsatishga ruxsat berish uchun foydalanish mumkin.','Choose which address to save as the shipping address for local pickup orders.' => 'Mahalliy olib ketish buyurtmalari uchun yuk manzili sifatida saqlash uchun qaysi manzilni tanlang.','Save the selected pickup location' => 'Tanlangan olib ketish joyini saqlang','Save same as the billing address' => 'Hisob-kitob manzili bilan bir xil saqlang','Do not save any shipping address' => 'Hech qanday yuk manzilini saqlamang','Company name field for shipping address' => 'Yuk tashish manzili uchun kompaniya nomi maydoni','Change visibility for the company name field for the shipping address section on the checkout form.' => 'Hisob-kitob shaklidagi etkazib berish manzili bo&#39;limi uchun kompaniya nomi maydonining ko&#39;rinishini o&#39;zgartiring.','If field is set as "optional", which is the default visibility state, no changes will be applied to let other plugins apply any changes they need.' => 'Agar maydon standart koʻrinish holati boʻlgan “ixtiyoriy” sifatida sozlangan boʻlsa, boshqa plaginlarga kerakli oʻzgarishlarni qoʻllash uchun hech qanday oʻzgarishlar qoʻllanilmaydi.','Hidden (remove field)' => 'Yashirin (maydonni olib tashlash)','Optional' => 'Ixtiyoriy','Required' => 'Majburiy','Add shipping phone field to the checkout form.' => 'To‘lov shakliga jo‘natma telefoni maydonini qo‘shing.','Choose in which step to display the shipping phone field.' => 'Yuborilgan telefon maydonini qaysi bosqichda ko&#39;rsatishni tanlang.','Contact step' => 'Aloqa bosqichi','Billing phone' => 'Hisob-kitob telefoni','Add billing phone field to the checkout form.' => 'To‘lov shakliga billing telefon maydonini qo‘shing.','Choose in which step to display the billing phone field.' => 'Billing telefon maydonini qaysi bosqichda ko&#39;rsatishni tanlang.','Enable international phone number format and validation for phone fields' => 'Xalqaro telefon raqamlari formatini va telefon maydonlari uchun tekshirishni yoqing','Format and validate phone numbers according to each country.' => 'Telefon raqamlarini har bir mamlakatga qarab formatlang va tasdiqlang.','Enable phone number validation based on country rules' => 'Mamlakat qoidalari asosida telefon raqamini tekshirishni yoqing','When disabled, the phone field validation will not check if country or area codes are valid for the country.' => 'Agar o&#39;chirilgan bo&#39;lsa, telefon maydonini tekshirish mamlakat yoki hudud kodlari mamlakat uchun haqiqiyligini tekshirmaydi.','Only show allowed countries for shipping or billing' => 'Yuk tashish yoki hisob-kitob qilish uchun faqat ruxsat berilgan mamlakatlarni ko&#39;rsatish','When enabled, only the countries allowed for shipping will be available in the shipping phone field, and only countries allowed for billing will be available for the billing phone field.' => 'Yoqilgan bo‘lsa, jo‘natish telefoni maydonida faqat jo‘natishga ruxsat berilgan mamlakatlar va billing telefon maydonida faqat hisob-kitob qilishga ruxsat berilgan mamlakatlar mavjud bo‘ladi.','Show country code beside the flag' => 'Bayroq yonida mamlakat kodini ko&#39;rsating','Show an example of a valid phone number inside phone fields' => 'Telefon maydonlarida haqiqiy telefon raqamiga misol ko&#39;rsating','Do not change placeholders' => 'To&#39;ldiruvchilarni o&#39;zgartirmang','Show if not defined' => 'Belgilanmagan bo&#39;lsa ko&#39;rsating','Always show' => 'Har doim ko&#39;rsating','Order notes' => 'Buyurtma eslatmalari','Define the visibility of the additional order notes field.' => 'Qo&#39;shimcha buyurtma eslatmalari maydonining ko&#39;rinishini belgilang.','Gift options' => 'Sovg&#39;a variantlari','Display gift message and other gift options at the checkout page' => 'To&#39;lov sahifasida sovg&#39;a xabari va boshqa sovg&#39;a variantlarini ko&#39;rsating','Allow customers to add a gift message and other gift related options to the order.' => 'Mijozlarga sovg&#39;a xabari va sovg&#39;a bilan bog&#39;liq boshqa variantlarni buyurtmaga qo&#39;shishga ruxsat bering.','Display the gift message fields always expanded' => 'Har doim kengaytirilgan sovg&#39;a xabari maydonlarini ko&#39;rsatish','Display the gift message as part of the order details table instead of a separate section' => 'Sovg&#39;a xabarini alohida bo&#39;lim o&#39;rniga buyurtma tafsilotlari jadvalining bir qismi sifatida ko&#39;rsating','This option affects the order confirmation page (thank you page) and order details on account pages, emails and packing slips.' => 'Ushbu parametr buyurtmani tasdiqlash sahifasiga (rahmat sahifasi) va hisob sahifalari, elektron pochta xabarlari va qadoqlash varaqlaridagi buyurtma tafsilotlariga ta&#39;sir qiladi.','Account matching' => 'Hisobni moslashtirish','Enable the account matching feature' => 'Hisobni moslashtirish funksiyasini yoqing','Associate the guest customer\'s orders with their existing account when an account already exists with the customer\'s contact details.' => 'Mijozning aloqa ma&#39;lumotlari bilan hisob allaqachon mavjud bo&#39;lsa, mehmon mijozning buyurtmalarini ularning mavjud hisobi bilan bog&#39;lang.','Display message when an account exists with the email address provided' => 'Ko&#39;rsatilgan elektron pochta manzili bilan hisob mavjud bo&#39;lganda xabarni ko&#39;rsatish','Replaces the account creation fields with a notification and option to log in. In some contexts, it might be recommended to leave this option disabled to protect the privacy of customers.' => 'Hisob yaratish maydonlarini bildirishnoma va tizimga kirish opsiyasi bilan almashtiradi. Baʼzi kontekstlarda mijozlarning maxfiyligini himoya qilish uchun ushbu parametrni oʻchirib qoʻyish tavsiya etilishi mumkin.','Dashboard' => 'Boshqaruv paneli','Integrations' => 'Integratsiyalar','No integrations available at the moment on this section. The options related to each plugin will only appear here if that plugin is activated.' => 'Ushbu bo&#39;limda hozircha integratsiya mavjud emas. Har bir plagin bilan bog&#39;liq variantlar faqat plagin faollashtirilgan bo&#39;lsa, bu yerda paydo bo&#39;ladi.','License keys' => 'Litsenziya kalitlari','No license keys options available at the moment on this section. The options related to each plugin or add-on will appear here when that plugin is activated.' => 'Ushbu bo&#39;limda hozirda litsenziya kalitlari variantlari mavjud emas. Har bir plagin yoki plaginga tegishli variantlar plagin faollashtirilganda shu yerda paydo bo&#39;ladi.','Visit our website for more information about our plugins and add-ons.' => 'Plaginlarimiz va plaginlarimiz haqida ko&#39;proq ma&#39;lumot olish uchun veb-saytimizga tashrif buyuring.','Order pay page' => 'Buyurtma to&#39;lash sahifasi','Order pay' => 'Buyurtma to&#39;lash','Enable order pay page optimizations' => 'Buyurtma toʻlovi sahifasini optimallashtirishni yoqing','Changes the layout of order pay page for existing orders pending payment from the customer.' => 'Mijozdan toʻlov kutilayotgan mavjud buyurtmalar uchun toʻlov sahifasi tartibini oʻzgartiradi.','Add widget areas to the order pay page' => 'Buyurtmani to&#39;lash sahifasiga vidjet maydonlarini qo&#39;shing','These widget areas are used to add trust symbols and trust badges on the order pay page.' => 'Bu vidjet maydonlari buyurtma toʻlovi sahifasiga ishonch belgilari va ishonch nishonlarini qoʻshish uchun ishlatiladi.','Thank you page & order details layout' => 'Rahmat sahifasi va buyurtma tafsilotlari tartibi','Order details optimizations' => 'Buyurtma tafsilotlarini optimallashtirish','Enable thank you page and order details optimizations' => 'Rahmat sahifasi va buyurtma tafsilotlarini optimallashtirishni yoqing','Changes the layout of order details on the thank you page and account pages.' => 'Rahmat sahifasi va hisob sahifalarida buyurtma tafsilotlari tartibini o&#39;zgartiradi.','Enable order details customizations on email notifications' => 'Elektron pochta xabarnomalarida buyurtma tafsilotlarini sozlashni yoqing','Display new sections and change order of sections on email notifications. Styles of order details on email notifications remain unchanged.' => 'Elektron pochta xabarnomalarida yangi bo&#39;limlarni ko&#39;rsatish va bo&#39;limlar tartibini o&#39;zgartirish. Elektron pochta xabarnomalarida buyurtma tafsilotlari uslublari o&#39;zgarishsiz qoladi.','Thank you page' => 'Rahmat sahifasi','These options affect the thank you page, also known as order received or order confirmation pages.' => 'Ushbu parametrlar buyurtma qabul qilingan yoki buyurtmani tasdiqlash sahifalari sifatida ham tanilgan rahmat sahifasiga ta&#39;sir qiladi.','Order details layout' => 'Buyurtma tafsilotlari tartibi','Display the order details with wide layout on the thank you page' => 'Rahmat sahifasida buyurtma tafsilotlarini keng tartib bilan ko&#39;rsating','Add widget areas to the thank you page' => 'Minnatdorchilik sahifasiga vidjet maydonlarini qo&#39;shing','These widget areas are used to add trust symbols and trust badges on the thank you page.' => 'Ushbu vidjet maydonlari rahmat sahifasiga ishonch belgilari va ishonch nishonlarini qo&#39;shish uchun ishlatiladi.','These options affect the thank you page , view order details on account pages and on email notifications.' => 'Ushbu parametrlar rahmat sahifasiga, hisob sahifalarida va elektron pochta xabarnomalarida buyurtma tafsilotlarini ko&#39;rishga ta&#39;sir qiladi.','Order actions' => 'Amallarni buyurtma qilish','Choose in which position to display the order actions.' => 'Buyurtma harakatlarini qaysi holatda ko&#39;rsatishni tanlang.','Inside the order overview' => 'Buyurtmaning umumiy ko&#39;rinishi ichida','After the order overview' => 'Buyurtmani ko&#39;rib chiqqandan so&#39;ng','After order sections' => 'Buyurtma bo&#39;limlaridan keyin','Order status' => 'Buyurtma holati','Display the order status progress bar' => 'Buyurtma holatining borishi satrini ko&#39;rsating','Choose in which position to display the section.' => 'Bo&#39;limni qaysi holatda ko&#39;rsatishni tanlang.','After the order overview and payment instructions' => 'Buyurtmani ko&#39;rib chiqish va to&#39;lov ko&#39;rsatmalaridan keyin','Before the order items section' => 'Buyurtma elementlari bo&#39;limidan oldin','Inside the order items section' => 'Buyurtma elementlari bo&#39;limi ichida','After the order items section' => 'Buyurtma elementlari bo&#39;limidan keyin','On the sidebar' => 'Yon panelda','Order downloads' => 'Yuklab olish uchun buyurtma','Gift message' => 'Sovg&#39;a xabari','Tools' => 'Asboblar','Troubleshooting' => 'Muammolarni bartaraf qilish; nosozliklarni TUZATISH','Debug options' => 'Nosozliklarni tuzatish imkoniyatlari','Debug mode' => 'Nosozliklarni tuzatish rejimi','Using debug mode affects the website performance. Only use this option while troubleshooting.' => 'Nosozliklarni tuzatish rejimidan foydalanish veb-sayt ishiga ta&#39;sir qiladi. Ushbu parametrdan faqat muammolarni bartaraf etishda foydalaning.','Load unminified assets' => 'Minimallashtirilgan aktivlarni yuklang','Enhanced select fields' => 'Kengaytirilgan tanlash maydonlari','Replace <code>select2</code> dropdown components with <code>TomSelect</code>' => '<code>select2</code> ochiladigan komponentlarini <code>TomSelect</code> bilan almashtiring','TomSelect is a simpler dropdown selection component which is less prone to errors than Select2, while offering the same features that are actually used on WooCommerce checkout pages.' => 'TomSelect - bu Select2 ga qaraganda xatolarga kamroq moyil bo&#39;lgan oddiy ochiladigan tanlash komponenti bo&#39;lib, aslida WooCommerce to&#39;lov sahifalarida ishlatiladigan bir xil xususiyatlarni taklif qiladi.','Fix automatic zoom-in on form fields' => 'Shakl maydonlarida avtomatik kattalashtirishni tuzating','Set <code>font-size</code> inside form fields to 16px' => 'Shakl maydonlari ichidagi <code>font-size</code> 16px qilib belgilang','When the font size inside form fields is smaller than 16px, Safari and other browsers might automatically zoom in on mobile devices to make the text easier to read. When this option is enabled, it will set the font size for inside the form fields to 16px on pages optimized by Fluid Checkout to avoid it zooming in.' => 'Shakl maydonlari ichidagi shrift o&#39;lchami 16px dan kichik bo&#39;lsa, Safari va boshqa brauzerlar matnni o&#39;qishni osonlashtirish uchun mobil qurilmalarni avtomatik ravishda kattalashtirishi mumkin. Ushbu parametr yoqilganda, u kattalashtirishni oldini olish uchun Fluid Checkout tomonidan optimallashtirilgan sahifalarda shakl maydonlari ichidagi shrift hajmini 16px qilib o&#39;rnatadi.','The shipping destination is always set to "Default to customer shipping address" when Fluid Checkout is activated. Customers can still provide different shipping and billing addresses during checkout, an option for setting the default billing address to be the same as the shipping address is available at WooCommerce > Settings > Fluid Checkout.' => 'Fluid Checkout yoqilganda, jo&#39;natiladigan manzil har doim &quot;Mijozning jo&#39;natish manzili bo&#39;yicha birlamchi&quot; ga o&#39;rnatiladi. Mijozlar to&#39;lov vaqtida turli xil yuk va hisob-kitob manzillarini taqdim etishlari mumkin, standart to&#39;lov manzilini etkazib berish manzili bilan bir xil qilib o&#39;rnatish imkoniyati WooCommerce &gt; Sozlamalar &gt; Fluid Checkout-da mavjud.','Fluid Checkout' => 'Suyuqlikni tekshirish','Settings' => 'Sozlamalar','Support' => 'Qo&#39;llab-quvvatlash','<a target="_blank" href="%s">Upgrade to PRO</a> to unlock more options.' => 'Koʻproq imkoniyatlarni ochish uchun <a target="_blank" href="%s">PRO versiyasiga yangilang</a> .','(PRO)' => '(PRO)','(experimental)' => '(eksperimental)','This is an experimental feature and may not work as expected with all themes and plugins. Use it with caution.' => 'Bu eksperimental xususiyatdir va barcha mavzular va plaginlar bilan kutilganidek ishlamasligi mumkin. Ehtiyotkorlik bilan foydalaning.','Confirm' => 'Tasdiqlang','Verify Phone Number' => 'Telefon raqamini tasdiqlang','Please verify your phone number.' => 'Iltimos, telefon raqamingizni tasdiqlang.','The Bluehost Plugin' => 'Bluehost plagini','Custom fields' => 'Maxsus maydonlar','Enable custom shipping email field' => 'Maxsus jo‘natma e-pochta maydonini yoqing','When enabled, the shipping email field from the Bluehost plugin will be added to the checkout form.' => 'Yoqilganda, Bluehost plaginidagi jo&#39;natma elektron pochta maydoni to&#39;lov shakliga qo&#39;shiladi.','Captcha Pro by BestWebSoft' => 'BestWebSoft tomonidan Captcha Pro','Captcha position' => 'Captcha pozitsiyasi','Define the position to display the captcha section. Some positions might not work depending on the captcha type chosen.' => 'Captcha qismini ko&#39;rsatish uchun joyni belgilang. Ba&#39;zi pozitsiyalar tanlangan captcha turiga qarab ishlamasligi mumkin.','Selecting a pickup point is required before proceeding.' => 'Davom etishdan oldin qabul qilish nuqtasini tanlash kerak.','Pickup point' => 'Qabul qilish punkti','Pickup point not selected yet.' => 'Qabul qilish nuqtasi hali tanlanmagan.','Pickup point:' => 'Qabul qilish nuqtasi:','Mailchimp for WooCommerce' => 'WooCommerce uchun Mailchimp','Subscribe checkbox' => 'Obuna bo&#39;lish katagiga belgi qo&#39;ying','Override the position for the subscribe checkbox on the checkout page and always display it on the contact step' => 'Hisob-kitob sahifasida obuna bo&#39;lish uchun belgini bekor qiling va uni har doim aloqa bosqichida ko&#39;rsating','Before Shipping Address' => 'Yuk tashishdan oldin manzil','(originally "%s")' => '(aslida &quot;%s&quot;)','After Shipping Address' => 'Yuk tashishdan keyin manzil','Selecting a collection point is required when shipping with FermoPoint.' => 'FermoPoint bilan jo&#39;natilayotganda yig&#39;ish nuqtasini tanlash talab qilinadi.','If checked informs typos in email to users. (This feature has been disabled because Fluid Checkout offers the feature. Changes to this option will not take effect)' => 'Belgilangan bo&#39;lsa, foydalanuvchilarga e-pochtadagi xatolar haqida xabar beradi. (Fluid Checkout funksiyani taklif qilgani uchun bu funksiya o‘chirib qo‘yilgan. Ushbu parametrga kiritilgan o‘zgartirishlar kuchga kirmaydi)','Enable Mail Check: (disabled feature)' => 'Pochta tekshiruvini yoqish: (o‘chirilgan xususiyat)','Carrier:' => 'Tashuvchi:','Sendinblue - WooCommerce Email Marketing' => 'Sendinblue - WooCommerce elektron pochta marketingi','Sign up checkbox position' => 'Ro&#39;yxatdan o&#39;tish katakchasi pozitsiyasi','Move the sign up checkbox to the contact step' => 'Ro&#39;yxatdan o&#39;tish katakchasini kontakt bosqichiga o&#39;tkazing','When enabled, the checkbox will be moved to the contact step independently of the display location defined in the Sendinblue plugin settings.' => 'Yoqilganda, belgilash katakchasi Sendinblue plagin sozlamalarida belgilangan displey joylashuvidan qat&#39;i nazar, kontakt bosqichiga o&#39;tkaziladi.','Theme Betheme' => 'Betheme mavzusi','Checkout progress' => 'Hisob-kitob jarayoni','Output the checkout steps section from Betheme on the checkout, cart and order received pages.' => 'Betheme-dan to&#39;lov bosqichlari bo&#39;limini to&#39;lov, savat va qabul qilingan buyurtma sahifalarida chiqaring.','Theme Fennik' => 'Mavzu Fennik','Breadcrumbs' => 'Non bo&#39;laklari','Output the breadcrumbs section from the Fennik theme when using Fluid Checkout header and footer.' => 'Fluid Checkout sarlavhasi va altbilgisidan foydalanganda Fennik mavzusidagi non sindirish bo&#39;limini chiqaring.','Theme Go' => 'Mavzu Go','My account layout' => 'Mening hisobim tartibi','Enable wide layout on "My account" page.' => '&quot;Mening hisobim&quot; sahifasida keng tartibni yoqing.','Theme Impreza' => 'Impreza mavzusi','Header' => 'Sarlavha','Spacing for site header at the checkout page (in pixels)' => 'Hisob-kitob sahifasida sayt sarlavhasi uchun interval (piksellarda)','Only applicable when using the Impreza theme header at the checkout page.' => 'Faqat to&#39;lov sahifasida Impreza mavzusi sarlavhasidan foydalanilganda amal qiladi.','Theme Kapee' => 'Mavzu Kapee','Output the checkout steps section from the Kapee theme on the checkout, cart and order received pages.' => 'Qabul qilingan varaqlar, savat va buyurtma sahifalarida Kapee mavzusidan chiqish bosqichlari bo&#39;limini chiqaring.','Theme Porto' => 'Porto mavzusi','Output the checkout steps section from the Porto theme on the checkout, cart and order received pages.' => 'To&#39;lov, savat va qabul qilingan buyurtma sahifalarida Porto mavzusidan chiqish bosqichlari bo&#39;limini chiqaring.','Theme Pressmart' => 'Mavzu Pressmart','Output the checkout steps section from the Pressmart theme on the checkout, cart and order received pages.' => 'To&#39;lov, savat va qabul qilingan buyurtma sahifalarida Pressmart mavzusidan chiqish bosqichlari bo&#39;limini chiqaring.','Theme The Gem' => 'Mavzu Gem','Output the checkout steps section from The Gem theme when using Fluid Checkout header and footer.' => 'Fluid Checkout sarlavhasi va altbilgisidan foydalanganda The Gem mavzusidagi to&#39;lov bosqichlari bo&#39;limini chiqaring.','Theme Woodmart' => 'Woodmart mavzusi','Output the checkout steps section from the Woodmart theme when using Fluid Checkout header and footer.' => 'Fluid Checkout sarlavhasi va altbilgisidan foydalanganda Woodmart mavzusidagi to&#39;lov bosqichlari bo&#39;limini chiqaring.','Checkout options' => 'Hisob-kitob opsiyalari','Disable the theme checkout options' => 'Mavzuni tekshirish parametrlarini o&#39;chiring','The options display product image, quantity field, remove button and link to product page added by the theme are disabled by default.' => 'Variantlar mahsulot tasviri, miqdor maydoni, oʻchirish tugmasi va mavzu boʻyicha qoʻshilgan mahsulot sahifasiga havolani koʻrsatish sukut boʻyicha oʻchirib qoʻyilgan.','Theme Atomion' => 'Mavzu Atomion','Order progress' => 'Buyurtmaning borishi','Display order progress from the theme' => 'Mavzu bo&#39;yicha buyurtma jarayonini ko&#39;rsatish','Display the form field labels visible on the page' => 'Sahifada ko&#39;rinadigan shakl maydoni teglarini ko&#39;rsating','It is recommended to keep this option enabled for a better user experience.' => 'Yaxshiroq foydalanuvchi tajribasi uchun ushbu parametrni yoqilgan holda saqlash tavsiya etiladi.','Theme ZK Nito' => 'Mavzu ZK Nito','Add extra fields to the checkout form' => 'To&#39;lov shakliga qo&#39;shimcha maydonlar qo&#39;shing','Adds an extra shipping email and shipping phone field to the shipping address section.' => 'Yuk tashish manzili bo&#39;limiga qo&#39;shimcha yuk e-pochtasi va yuk telefoni maydonini qo&#39;shadi.','Go to the home page' => 'Bosh sahifaga o&#39;ting','Skip to content' => 'Tarkibga oʻtish','Create an account' => 'Hisob ochish','Log in to your account' => 'Hisobingizga kiring','Already have an account?' => 'Hisobingiz bormi?','Logged in as %1$s. <a href="%2$s">Log out</a>' => '%1$s sifatida tizimga kirgan. <a href="%2$s">Chiqish</a>','Your order has a total amount due of %s. No further payment is needed.' => 'Buyurtmangizning umumiy miqdori %s. Qo&#39;shimcha to&#39;lov talab qilinmaydi.','Close and continue with checkout' => 'Yoping va to&#39;lovni davom eting','Continue' => 'Davom eting','Parcel terminal' => 'Posilka terminali','<p>This widget has been replaced by Fluid Checkout. </p><p>When using Fluid Checkout, the checkout page needs to use the original WooCommerce shortcode <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code> to work properly.</p><p>For more information, visit the Fluid Checkout documentation.</p>' => '<p>Ushbu vidjet Fluid Checkout bilan almashtirildi.</p><p> Fluid Checkout-dan foydalanganda, to&#39;g&#39;ri ishlashi uchun to&#39;lov sahifasi asl WooCommerce qisqa kodidan <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code> foydalanishi kerak.</p><p> Qo&#39;shimcha ma&#39;lumot olish uchun Fluid Checkout hujjatlariga tashrif buyuring.</p>','Theme The7' => 'Mavzu 7','Additional header sections' => 'Qo&#39;shimcha sarlavha bo&#39;limlari','Output additional header sections if enabled in the theme settings.' => 'Mavzu sozlamalarida yoqilgan bo&#39;lsa, qo&#39;shimcha sarlavha bo&#39;limlarini chiqaring.','More information' => 'Batafsil ma&#39;lumot','Pick a Locker' => 'Shkafni tanlang','Page template' => 'Sahifa shabloni','Use `Order confirmation` page template for block-based themes' => 'Blokka asoslangan mavzular uchun “Buyurtmani tasdiqlash” sahifasi shablonidan foydalaning','Only applies when using a block-based theme.' => 'Faqat blokga asoslangan mavzudan foydalanilganda amal qiladi.','WooCommerce Stripe Gateway' => 'WooCommerce Stripe Gateway','Payment form' => 'To&#39;lov shakli','Apply styles to the Stripe payment form fields' => 'Stripe toʻlov formasi maydonlariga uslublarni qoʻllang','When enabled, Fluid Checkout will apply styles optimized for compatibility with the plugin. You may want to disable this if you are using custom styles for the Stripe payment form fields.' => 'Yoqilganda, Fluid Checkout plagin bilan moslik uchun optimallashtirilgan uslublarni qo&#39;llaydi. Agar siz Stripe toʻlov formasi maydonlari uchun maxsus uslublardan foydalanayotgan boʻlsangiz, buni oʻchirib qoʻyishingiz mumkin.','Theme Nyture' => 'Nyture mavzusi','Output the checkout steps section from the Nyture theme when using Fluid Checkout.' => 'Fluid Checkout dan foydalanayotganda Nyture mavzusidagi to&#39;lov bosqichlari bo&#39;limini chiqaring.','Maybe be forced as "required" if the billing address section is displayed after the shipping address section, and the billing phone field is set as "required. This is needed to ensure the shipping address can be copied to the billing address when that option is checked.' => 'Toʻlov manzili boʻlimi yetkazib berish manzili boʻlimidan keyin koʻrsatilsa va hisob-kitob telefoni maydoni “majburiy” sifatida oʻrnatilsa, “talab qilinadi” deb majburlash mumkin. Bu variant belgilansa, joʻnatish manzilini toʻlov manziliga koʻchirish mumkinligini taʼminlash uchun kerak.','Maybe be forced as "required" if the billing address section is displayed after the billing address section, and the billing phone field is set as "required. This is needed to ensure the billing address can be copied to the billing address when that option is checked.' => 'Hisob-kitob manzili boʻlimidan keyin toʻlov manzili boʻlimi koʻrsatilsa va billing telefon maydoni “majburiy” sifatida oʻrnatilgan boʻlsa, “zarur” deb majburlash mumkin. Bu variant belgilansa, hisob-kitob manzilini toʻlov manziliga koʻchirish mumkinligini taʼminlash uchun kerak.','Allows customers to make payments for orders that are either created manually by the store admin or not completed during checkout.' => 'Mijozlarga do&#39;kon administratori tomonidan qo&#39;lda yaratilgan yoki to&#39;lov vaqtida tugallanmagan buyurtmalar uchun to&#39;lovlarni amalga oshirish imkonini beradi.','The plugin WooCommerce Checkout Manager by Quadlayers is not compatible with Fluid Checkout' => 'Plagin WooCommerce Checkout Manager by Quadlayers Fluid Checkout bilan mos kelmaydi','Company name field for billing address' => 'Hisob-kitob manzili uchun kompaniya nomi maydoni','Change visibility for the company name field for the billing address section on the checkout form.' => 'To‘lov shaklidagi hisob-kitob manzili bo‘limi uchun kompaniya nomi maydonining ko‘rinishini o‘zgartiring.','Theme Bookshelf' => 'Mavzu kitob javoni','Output the checkout steps section from the Bookshelf theme when using Fluid Checkout.' => 'Fluid Checkout-dan foydalanganda Bookshelf mavzusidan to&#39;lov bosqichlari bo&#39;limini chiqaring.','Account password' => 'Hisob paroli','An account will be created with the information provided at checkout when completing the order.' => 'Buyurtmani to&#39;ldirishda to&#39;lov vaqtida taqdim etilgan ma&#39;lumotlar bilan hisob yaratiladi.','Choose the style of the progress bar.' => 'Harakat paneli uslubini tanlang.','Bars' => 'Barlar','Theme Ireca' => 'Ireca mavzusi','WooCommerce page layout' => 'WooCommerce sahifa tartibi','Force wide layout on WooCommerce pages' => 'WooCommerce sahifalarida keng tartibni majburlash','This ensures the content section is not too narrow on WooCommerce pages including checkout, cart, order received, order pay and account pages.' => 'Bu WooCommerce sahifalarida kontent bo&#39;limi juda tor bo&#39;lmasligini ta&#39;minlaydi, shu jumladan to&#39;lov, savat, qabul qilingan buyurtma, buyurtma to&#39;lovi va hisob sahifalari.','Button label for applying coupon codesApply' => 'Murojaat qiling','Checkout step titleContact' => 'Aloqa','Checkout step titleShipping' => 'yuk tashish; yetkazib berish','Checkout step titleBilling' => 'Hisob-kitob','Checkout step titlePayment' => 'To&#39;lov','Checkout substep change link labelChange' => 'O&#39;zgartirish','Checkout substep save link labelSave changes' => 'O&#39;zgarishlarni saqlang','Substep review textNone.' => 'Yo&#39;q.','Substep review field format%1$s' => '%1$s','Substep review field format: with label%2$s: %1$s' => '%2$s: %1$s','Image uploader.No image selected.' => 'Hech qanday rasm tanlanmagan.','Settings sectionCart' => 'Arava','Settings sectionOrder pay' => 'Buyurtma to&#39;lash','Settings sectionThank you' => 'rahmat','Settings section titleIntegrations' => 'Integratsiyalar','Settings section titleLicense keys' => 'Litsenziya kalitlari','Captcha positionBefore place order section' => 'Buyurtma berishdan oldin bo&#39;lim','Captcha positionBefore place order button' => 'Buyurtma berishdan oldin tugma','No shipping 